    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.integration.uml.derivedfeatures.activityGroupContainedEdge pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as ActivityGroupContainedEdgeMatch.

    Original source: 

     @Surrogate(feature = "containedEdge")
 @QueryExplorer(checked = false)
 pattern activityGroupContainedEdge(source: ActivityGroup, target: ActivityEdge)
 {
     // opposite of ActivityGroup.containedEdge
     find activityEdgeInGroup(target, source);
 }
